{"tid":1430722,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"主線係政權 副線係小強","createTime":"2019-08-07T21:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T21:55:17.000Z","uid":166591,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e91ccd5f21b61a21deea786607d055914ad0b0c2","tid":1430722,"uid":166591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:50:56.000Z","msg":"我地要做既係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">令班仆街驚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n點先可以做到？<br />\n對付港共：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搞西環</span></span><br />\n對付小強：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搞宿舍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先講主線政權<br />\n你睇下71衝完立法會，個政府有無驚過？<br />\n驚呀，係擔心嗰3塊玻璃咋<br />\n但721中聯辦<br />\n淆到連北京都開記招<br />\n所以，主戰場唔該直接搞西環<br />\n<br />\n其次係副線小強<br />\n留意到每次落區做運動都會好亂<br />\n近既有8.3 去到尖沙咀又嗌去紅隧之後又有啲人去翻mk<br />\n而之前每次落到區，前線最激都只係死守<br />\n（而死守有個問題，就係不斷有兄弟會被捕送頭）<br />\n因為<span style=\"color: red;\">就算想衝，都無一個地標可以衝</span><br />\n所以，與其死守，不如快閃衝佢老味，然後全身而退<br />\n而落區要撚小強既話，宿舍絕對係不二之選<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">禍必及妻兒</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">話「衝佢老味」唔係真係要「衝」，大家諗下點樣搞鳩到佢地</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然遍地開花同和理非都好重要，所以抱歉呢個po只係講緊<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武要衝嘅地標</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟只係匯集由6.9開始見到嘅嘢，俾少少戰術建議<br />\n有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2572eafc1305f2293f1e91798cb3621fc2ffa59d","tid":1430722,"uid":166591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:53:10.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78af875bc418e7c5fdafe4316943e2b5b6e0ac1f","tid":1430722,"uid":166591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fb4b42b1ddb140045adfe65f442e33314a63bb","tid":1430722,"uid":166591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}